## Windsurf-specific behavior

- Default to MCP-first patterns; jpcite value flows via API/MCP/static docs, not UI.
- When asked to scaffold a new feature, lean on the existing `scripts/generate_*_pages.py` family rather than inventing a new template runner.
- When refactoring search, account for the FTS5 trigram false-positive on single-kanji overlaps (`税` matching `税額控除` and `ふるさと納税`).
- When proposing observability, route to `monitoring/` + `analytics/` + `site/assets/rum.js` rather than a new vendor.
- When proposing payment plumbing, do not bypass `consent_collection` Stripe footgun — use `custom_text.submit.message` for the ToS link.

## Pre-deploy gate

- `.venv/bin/ruff check` targets sync with `scripts/distribution_manifest.yml`
- `.venv/bin/pytest` full
- `mypy src/`
- `mkdocs build --strict`
- OpenAPI regen + `scripts/check_distribution_manifest_drift.py`
- Smoke test post-deploy: sleep ≥60s, `curl --max-time ≥30s` (Fly p99 swap latency)

